能量方程的其他形式
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
动能方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
以 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{u}$
\end_inset

 点乘“非守恒型”动量方程（即 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：Navier--Stokes：非守恒型：向量型"

\end_inset

 第二行，暂不代入 
\begin_inset Formula $\Dyad{\sigma}=\Dyad{\tau}-p\Dyad{1}$
\end_inset

）得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{u}\vdot\rho\Dt{\vec{u}}=\vec{u}\vdot\left(\divg\Dyad{\sigma}+\vec{b}\right)
\]

\end_inset

并代入物质导数的性质 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：物质导数：线性性质"

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{u}\vdot\rho\Dt{\vec{u}}=\rho\Dt(\vec{u}\vdot\vec{u}/2)=\rho\Dt(\abs{\vec{u}}^{2}/2)
\]

\end_inset

即得描述“比动能 (specific kinetic energy)”变化率的“动能方程”：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\rho\Dt(\abs{\vec{u}}^{2}/2)=\vec{u}\vdot\left(\divg\Dyad{\sigma}+\vec{b}\right)\label{eq:流动方程：动能方程}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
内能方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
根据 
\begin_inset Formula $\Dt$
\end_inset

 的线性性质 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：物质导数：线性性质"

\end_inset

 及 
\begin_inset Formula $e_{0}=e+\abs{\vec{u}}^{2}/2$
\end_inset

，只需从“非守恒型”能量方程（即 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：Navier--Stokes：非守恒型：向量型"

\end_inset

 第三行）中减去动能方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：动能方程"

\end_inset

，即得描述“比内能 (specific internal energy)”变化率的“内能方程”：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\rho\Dt{e} & =\rho\Dt{e_{0}}-\rho\Dt(\abs{\vec{u}}^{2}/2)\\
 & =\divg(\Dyad{\sigma}\vdot\vec{u})-\vec{u}\vdot\left(\divg\Dyad{\sigma}\right)-\divg\vec{q}+j
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

第二行的前两项还可以写成更紧凑的形式。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[张量内积]
\end_layout

\end_inset

任意两个二阶张量 
\begin_inset Formula $\Dyad{A}=A_{ik}\vec{e}_{i}\vec{e}_{k}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\Dyad{B}=B_{ik}\vec{e}_{i}\vec{e}_{k}$
\end_inset

 的内积定义为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Dyad{A}\DyadDot\Dyad{B}=A_{ik}B_{ik}
\]

\end_inset

这里约定：重复的下标表示求和。 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
与“力（向量）与速度（向量）的内积表示功率”类似，“应力（张量）与应变率（张量）的内积”也具有功率的量纲。在流体力学中，主要考虑 
\begin_inset Formula $\Dyad{\sigma},\Dyad{\tau}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\grad\vec{u},\Dyad{E}$
\end_inset

 的内积：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\Dyad{1}\DyadDot\Dyad{E} & =\divg\vec{u}\\
\Dyad{\sigma}\DyadDot\left(\grad\vec{u}\right) & =\divg(\Dyad{\sigma}\vdot\vec{u})-\vec{u}\vdot\left(\divg\Dyad{\sigma}\right)\\
 & =\Dyad{\sigma}\DyadDot\Dyad{E}=\Dyad{\tau}\DyadDot\Dyad{E}-p\divg\vec{u}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
于是内能方程可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}\rho\Dt{e} & =\Dyad{\sigma}\DyadDot\left(\grad\vec{u}\right)-\divg\vec{q}+j\\
 & =\Dyad{\tau}\DyadDot\Dyad{E}-p\divg\vec{u}-\divg\vec{q}+j
\end{aligned}
\label{eq:流动方程：内能方程}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark*
黏性力做功会使控制体内的内能（温度）增加。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
压力方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于理想气体（
\begin_inset Formula $p=\rho RT$
\end_inset

），比内能 
\begin_inset Formula $e$
\end_inset

 与压力 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 有如下关系
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
e=\frac{RT}{\gamma-1}=\frac{p/\rho}{\gamma-1}\implies\rho\Dt{e}=\frac{\Dt{p}-(p/\rho)\Dt{\rho}}{\gamma-1}=\frac{\Dt{p}+p\divg\vec{u}}{\gamma-1}
\]

\end_inset

将其代入内能方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：内能方程"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 并将压力项移到等号左边，即得描述压力变化的“压力方程”：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{\Dt{p}+\gamma p\divg\vec{u}}{\gamma-1}=\Dyad{\tau}\DyadDot\Dyad{E}-\divg\vec{q}+j\label{eq:流动方程：压力方程}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
熵方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将“比体积 (specific volume)” 
\begin_inset Formula $v=\rho^{-1}$
\end_inset

 代入“非守恒型”质量方程（即 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：Navier--Stokes：非守恒型：向量型"

\end_inset

 第一行）可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\divg\vec{u}=-\rho^{-1}\Dt{\rho}=-v\Dt{v^{-1}}=v^{-1}\Dt{v}=\rho\Dt{v}
\]

\end_inset

将其代入内能方程（即 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:流动方程：内能方程"

\end_inset

 第二行），并利用“热力学第一定律”：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{e}=T\dd{s}-p\implies\Dt{e}=T\Dt{s}-p\Dt{v}
\]

\end_inset

可以得到描述“比熵 (specific entropy)”变化率的“熵方程”：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\rho T\Dt{s}=\Dyad{\tau}\DyadDot\Dyad{E}-\divg\vec{q}+j\label{eq:流动方程：熵方程}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark*
黏性力做功会使控制体内的熵增加，因此相应的物理过程是“不可逆的 (irreversible)”。
\end_layout

